&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction &lt;a href="#introduction" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Big resolution with small screens is more and more common and we&amp;rsquo;re facing a problem on fonts visualization. We have a lot of non adapted fonts for retina display, even if most of them are not so bad. The solution is to install additional fonts to replace the default one. One of the best one I&amp;rsquo;ve seen is &lt;a href="https://www.infinality.net/blog/" rel="external" target="_blank">Infinality fonts&lt;svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path fill="currentColor" d="M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hide an Open Application from the Dock and Switcher</title><link>https://wiki.deimos.fr/Cacher_une_application_ouverte_du_dock_et_du_switcher/</link><pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2008 07:16:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://wiki.deimos.fr/Cacher_une_application_ouverte_du_dock_et_du_switcher/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction &lt;a href="#introduction" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>If you want to use software that must remain open all the time but you don&amp;rsquo;t want to have its icon in your Dock or in the switcher (Cmd + Tab), it&amp;rsquo;s possible, though it doesn&amp;rsquo;t always work in all cases.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites &lt;a href="#prerequisites" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>There aren&amp;rsquo;t many prerequisites since the only thing you&amp;rsquo;ll need to be careful about is that before doing the following steps, your application must be closed.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>